By":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:52:53.000Z","msg":"From 氣象巴<br />\n<br />\n#公眾安全情報 #各區情況整合 <br />\n<br />\n1850更新<br />\n<br />\n灣仔區 4️⃣<br />\n⚠️防暴於銅鑼灣站展開拘捕行動，現場有警民對峙。<br />\n⚠️防暴曾於軒尼詩道、波斯富街交界展示黑旗。<br />\n<br />\n中西區 5️⃣<br />\n🛑防暴於雪廠街一帶展開截查及拘捕行動。<br />\n<br />\n#公共交通情報 #MTR <br />\n<br />\n🚇中環、灣仔站已經關閉。"},{"pid":"09a75b1425805bbf89a0c424d3ba1156b619d027","tid":1552492,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c47822cc9c275ae7e90a0458378826f0a12ca784","tid":1552492,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:52:06.000Z","msg":"From 103<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CVnCQkk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCVnCQkk.jpg&h=4aa10044&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9350d1eb370befb2a66eba9901ac2a93d05d32a","tid":1552492,"uid":97788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:53:12.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣大量防暴、天后巴士總站有防暴"},{"pid":"c78dbdd540c2c49c25870231c961b32c51961d5b","tid":1552492,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"From scout<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#灣仔 <br />\n1850 灣仔莊士敦道100防暴狗拆rb<br />\n<br />\n#灣仔 <br />\n1852 7籠2衝駛過灣仔電腦城<br />\n<br />\n#中環 <br />\n1845 ifc 外過15狗車standby"},{"pid":"a469d7966638946474f8d64f263b2e9bdf5ebac8","tid":1552492,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />郭生"},{"pid":"ff4f63b5bbfa2a04d8b46dba47656cbcb5580207","tid":1552492,"uid":138116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:54:24.000Z","msg":"天后好多狗車"},{"pid":"14c32303751668f59389787502830265bc74aa2b","tid":1552492,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:54:53.000Z","msg":"From 背水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【港島區即時地圖及路況目測 1852】<br />\n<br />\n#中環 至 #中半山<br />\n1840 干諾道中往金鐘方向交易廣場橋底 約25警車 待命<br />\n1840 干諾道中大會堂 平靜無警<br />\n<br />\n#金鐘<br />\n1833 高等法院 至少7eu正清除路障向灣仔出發<br />\n1832 金鐘站內 約50防暴 往c出口金鐘廊離開 配有旗手 橡膠子彈槍及催淚彈槍<br />\n1835 金鐘站內A出口 約20軍裝 戒備<br />\n1841 金鐘道警總外 150防暴 沿軒尼詩道及皇后大道東往灣仔方向推進<br />\n1842 干諾道中中信橋 1eu 駛往中環方向<br />\n1844 金鐘道皇后大道東交界 4衝鋒車 4運員車往灣仔方向行駛<br />\n1845 金鐘各出口 平靜 無警<br />\n1845 干諾道中中信橋 1eu 駛入添美道<br />\n<br />\n#灣仔 <br />\n1832 鵝頸橋向銅鑼灣方向 5豬籠1EU 行駛<br />\n1832 馬師道 1籠車轉入馬師道<br />\n1837 灣仔站閘內 約30 防暴 10便衣 戒備<br />\n1839 盧岬道一帶 平靜無警<br />\n1839 灣仔消防局 1運員 停泊<br />\n1842 解放軍營門外 平靜<br />\n1844 軒尼詩道軍器廠街4運員4EU 沿軒尼詩道往灣仔方向<br />\n<br />\n#銅鑼灣<br />\n1836 希慎利園山道 2運員車停泊 載有防暴 防暴現往SOGO方向<br />\n1841 銅鑼灣地鐵站b出口 大量防暴配戴豬嘴入地鐵站內<br />\n1845 銅鑼灣 堅拿道天橋 2EU 駛往銅鑼灣方向<br />\n<br />\n#炮台山<br />\n1838 英皇道往天后方向 大量警車 行駛"},{"pid":"cd84a16a0060c9ff968597e27f7f965e3d1c78ed","tid":1552492,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:54:56.000Z","msg":"郭富城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7a2f4aa7b2f77ccaf7392a2565ed9cec76738a","tid":1552492,"uid":186,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mO4d78c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmO4d78c.jpg&h=42e4bb26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1852 #灣仔 #軒尼詩道 <br />\n警方設立防線。 <br />\n#now"},{"pid":"79e016a0302fb5c00284a1d6c690c361ec021dcc","tid":1552492,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/08/185621_c55550c8637f9b097d8f6ae9e7280ada.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F08%2F185621_c55550c8637f9b097d8f6ae9e7280ada.jpeg&h=ead28ee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1849 #銅鑼灣地鐵站<br />\n有防暴人員持槍戒備， 並設立封鎖線。<br />\n#蘋果"},{"pid":"23e80165d26fe1631511c2bca91b851946bc7d6a","tid":1552492,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:57:09.000Z","msg":"#銅鑼灣 <br />\n1852 鵝頸橋 3eu1豬籠經過 估計往銅記方向"},{"pid":"c6ef028d806a4f353d20315dfda673d02971b451","tid":1552492,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:57:25.000Z","msg":"#銅鑼灣 <br />\n1854  Hysan後面4架狗車"},{"pid":"c4dc8987779d740321c026954bf3c244b2aa016f","tid":1552492,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:58:09.000Z","msg":"18:45 各交通要點安全情報<br />\n<br />\n✅ 暫時安全地點<br />\n葵興站<br />\n美孚站西鐵月台<br />\n灣仔碼頭<br />\n香港站（入面）<br />\n紅隧來回<br />\n長洲碼頭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n⚠️ 不安全地點<br />\n紅磡站‼️‼️（由安全變不安全）<br />\n銅鑼灣站 有防暴衝入站<br />\n灣仔站 有防暴<br />\n炮台山站 站外有防暴<br />\n中環交易廣場巴士總站 有百防暴速龍<br />\n西隧港島入口 有rb查車‼️<br />\n金鐘站 有超過50防暴<br />\n旺角站 多個出口有popo<br />\n油塘站 有防暴<br />\n尖沙咀碼頭 多狗車"},{"pid":"91a6c789b7182c57be7f0394ace6874d53b8c3b2","tid":1552492,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:58:25.000Z","msg":"18:50 電車服務由維園至港澳碼頭暫停"},{"pid":"a9b14dde99cde6194578a787ff94af6990b05b6f","tid":1552492,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f173dcc501510a1ef5679309706e51f8aeb6c5","tid":1552492,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:58:40.000Z","msg":"#灣仔 <br />\n1855 逾百防暴防線推過了洛克道街市"},{"pid":"e76d15388f8737ce9492cfa0fad415dca5ea31cb","tid":1552492,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:59:30.000Z","msg":"應該又拉一堆"},{"pid":"d79c9b493b96d974489